WPML-Compatible-themes-1.png 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce several compatible WPML themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/upside-multi-purpose-wordpress-theme/14033192\" target=\"_blank\">Upside</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/movement-personal-blog-wordpress-theme/14102366\" target=\"_blank\">Movement</a>, <a href=\"https://lazycatthemes.com/fika/\" target=\"_blank\">Fika</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/liberty-your-political-wordpress-theme/15341403\" target=\"_blank\">Liberty</a>, <a href=\"https://www.lyrathemes.com/kale-pro/\" target=\"_blank\">Kale</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/zoner-real-estate-wordpress-theme/9099226\" target=\"_blank\">Zoner</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Upside</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Upside is the ultimate responsive multi-purpose WordPress theme designed for any kind of business websites, from small to medium-sized enterprises.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/upside-multi-purpose-wordpress-theme/14033192\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Upside</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Movement</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Movement is a personal blog WordPress responsive theme with masonry grid created using HTML5 &#038; SCSS, mobile optimized &#038; retina ready.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/movement-personal-blog-wordpress-theme/14102366\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Movement</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Fika</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Fika is a feature-rich and versatile theme optimized for WordPress food blogs</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://lazycatthemes.com/fika/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Fika</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Liberty</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Theme is dedicated to political parties and candidates.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/liberty-your-political-wordpress-theme/15341403\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Liberty</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kale</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Kale Pro is a simple but feature-filled food blog WordPress theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://www.lyrathemes.com/kale-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Kale</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Zoner</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Zoner is a Real Estate WordPress theme with unique functionality, design and features.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/zoner-real-estate-wordpress-theme/9099226\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Zoner</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=A2TndbGG9SA:GY5npMjQBL0:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=A2TndbGG9SA:GY5npMjQBL0:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=A2TndbGG9SA:GY5npMjQBL0:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=A2TndbGG9SA:GY5npMjQBL0:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=A2TndbGG9SA:GY5npMjQBL0:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=A2TndbGG9SA:GY5npMjQBL0:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/A2TndbGG9SA\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://wpml.org/2016/11/compatible-themes-nov-2016-2/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"https://wpml.org/2016/11/compatible-themes-nov-2016-2/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a: