d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-300x84.png 300w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1-150x42.png 150w, https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/WPML-Compatible-themes-1.png 568w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce several compatible WPML themes.</p>\n<p>The themes are, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/aadi-construction-wordpress-theme/17271521\" target=\"_blank\">Aadi</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/hotel-old-town-wordpress-theme/17269049\" target=\"_blank\">PE Hotel</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/esquare-responsive-wordpress-blog-theme/13895642\" target=\"_blank\">Esquare</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/bellevue-hotel-bed-breakfast-booking-theme/12482898\" target=\"_blank\">Bellevue</a>, <a href=\"http://www.jawtemplates.com/jaw-portfolio/gdn-magazine-blog-video-theme/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">GDayNews</a>, <a href=\"https://lazycatthemes.com/kaleidoscope/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kaleidoscope</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/hello-friday-elegant-lifestyle-blog-theme/17695139\" target=\"_blank\">Hello Friday</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/focuson-business-wordpress-theme/15611214\" target=\"_blank\">Focuson</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/labomba-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/6106367\" target=\"_blank\">Labomba</a>, <a href=\"https://herothemes.com/themes/knowall-wordpress-knowledge-base/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">KnowAll</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/basic/\" target=\"_blank\">Basic</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/minishop-multipurpose-minimal-ecommerce-marketplace-wordpress-theme/17507806\" target=\"_blank\">Minishop</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/thegem-creative-multipurpose-highperformance-wordpress-theme/16061685\" target=\"_blank\">TheGem</a>, <a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/moment-creative-wordpress-blog-theme/13302979\" target=\"_blank\">Moment</a></p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/\">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/\">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href=\"https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/\">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Aadi</h2>\n<blockquote><p>AADI is a comprehensive wordpress theme designed catering to the needs of Architecture, Engineering and other construction related services.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/aadi-construction-wordpress-theme/17271521\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Aadi</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">PE Hotel</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Powerful hotel WordPress theme offers you the ready solution for any hotel,motel, guest house or any other hotel industry sites.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/hotel-old-town-wordpress-theme/17269049\" ta