ulti-purpose e-Commerce websites</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/minishop-multipurpose-minimal-ecommerce-marketplace-wordpress-theme/17507806\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Minishop</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">TheGem</h2>\n<blockquote><p>TheGem is a versatile, responsive, high-performance WordPress theme with a modern creative design to suit a multitude of creative uses for building websites.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/thegem-creative-multipurpose-highperformance-wordpress-theme/16061685\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase TheGem</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feature\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Moment</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Simple WordPress blog theme designed to highlight visual content in a creative way across all mobile and desktop devices.</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button download-button vt-p\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/moment-creative-wordpress-blog-theme/13302979\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Purchase Moment</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=XtEJiU9eJVY:mt7LrYrSHN8:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=XtEJiU9eJVY:mt7LrYrSHN8:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=XtEJiU9eJVY:mt7LrYrSHN8:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=XtEJiU9eJVY:mt7LrYrSHN8:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=XtEJiU9eJVY:mt7LrYrSHN8:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=XtEJiU9eJVY:mt7LrYrSHN8:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/XtEJiU9eJVY\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=